description: This crunchy stir-fry is a quick to cook making it a perfect midweek dinner option.
keywords: Noodle stir-fry,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Dairy free
name: Turkey Noodle Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 300g noodles, cooked as per packet instructions
1 medium red onion, peeled and sliced

recipeInstructions.text: Cook the noodles as per pack instructions and then drain and leave to one side. Tear the cooked turkey to shreds or chop into bite size portions.
Heat up a wok with some canola oil and fry the onion, garlic and pepper for 5 minutes. Add the green beans and bean sprouts and fry for 1 more minute.
Add the rest of the ingredients and cook out for a further 7 minutes tossing regularly before serving.
